WHAT IT IS

You're gonna die.
Your phone won't.

500GB of screenshots. 10,000 memes. Inside jokes nobody will understand. 
The real story of what happened that night. Your actual personality, compressed 
into folders labeled "if u see this im dead lol"

Where does it go? Your next of kin who doesn't know your password? 
Apple's iCloud cemetery? Nowhere?

Fuck that.

DEAD DROP is a dead man's switch for your digital soul.

