THE PRODUCT

DROP VAULTS

Create drops. Load them with whatever.

- THE VAULT â€“ Too spicy for alive-you
- RECEIPTS â€“ The truth, timestamped
- GROUPCHAT NUKE â€“ Your magnum opus, delivered to the thread
- CONFESSIONAL â€“ Clear your conscience, unclear your browser history
- TIMEBOMB â€“ Scheduled for your funeral, your birthday, whenever

Each vault = its own release schedule, its own executors, its own trigger.

EXECUTORS

Pick who hits the button.

Not your family. Not your lawyer. Your friend who would actually do it. 
The groupchat. The ex who deserves to know. Nobody, and let the timer run out.

They get keys. Not all keys. Just theirs.

When you go dark, they decide: was it a vacation or the big one?

TRIGGERS

AUTO:
- 90 days offline (soft)
- 180 days offline (probable)
- 1 year offline (yeah it happened)
- Apple Health flatline (dark mode activated)

MANUAL:
- Death certificate upload
- 3/5 executor vote
- "Fuck it, send it now" button (while alive, for chaos)

SCHEDULED:
- Your funeral (they'll be checking their phones anyway)
- Your birthday, 5 years later
- New Year's 2050
- When you would've turned 69

72-hour failsafe on everything. If you're actually alive, you can cancel 
from any device. If you're not... it's too late anyway.

