THE EXPERIENCE

WHILE ALIVE:

Monthly "PROOF OF LIFE"
Check-in or your countdown starts. Miss it = executors get a ping.
Gamified because anxiety is better with points.

VAULT PREVIEW MODE
See your own memorial. Cringe. Edit. Repeat.
"You'll reach approximately 247 people. That's more than your last post."

COLLABORATIVE DROPS
Invite friends to co-author a time capsule.
"Remember when we..." but make it a legal document.

