GO-TO-MARKET (THE CHAOS PLAN)

PHASE 1: STEALTH
Build it. Tell nobody. Invite 100 people. Watch what happens.

PHASE 2: STUNT
The fake death. The viral drop. The media freakout.
Articles write themselves:
- "Is This Death App Genius or Dystopian?"
- "Gen Z Startup Wants to Disrupt Dying"
- "I Tried the Death Meme App and Now I'm Existential"

PHASE 3: DROPS
Weekly invite waves. Waitlist grows. FOMO intensifies.
People asking "when's my drop?"

PHASE 4: UBIQUITY
Becomes the standard.
"Did you set up your Dead Drop yet?"
Like asking if someone has a will, but less boring.

