WHY THIS EXISTS

Because death is the one thing capitalism hasn't fully colonized yet.

Because your digital life is worth more than your login credentials.

Because funeral homes charge $10k for a box and we charge $49 for forever.

Because everyone jokes about dying but nobody actually plans for it.

Because your memes deserve to outlive you.

Because this is less weird than cryogenics.

Because we made it and now it exists.

